  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators proposed to compare a modified Prolonged Exposure intervention to treatment
      as usual within a hospitalized injured trauma survivor sample, to determine with this
      intervention could prevent the development of PTSD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
